org.gradoop.flink.model.impl.operators.keyedgrouping.labelspecific

Class UnlabeledGroupAggregatorWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gradoop.flink.model.impl.operators.keyedgrouping.labelspecific.UnlabeledGroupAggregatorWrapper
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, AggregateDefaultValue, AggregateFunction

    public class UnlabeledGroupAggregatorWrapper
extends Object
    A wrapper for aggregate functions that will only return the increment of elements that are not contained in any label group.

      • postAggregate

        public PropertyValue postAggregate(PropertyValue result)
        Description copied from interface: AggregateFunction
        Compute the final result after the aggregation step was completed. This method may be implemented if the aggregate function uses some internal aggregate value not equal to the result.
        The default implementation of this method does nothing, it returns the result unchanged.
        This method will not be called when the aggregate value is null.
        Specified by:
